<Base title="Free Mentoring" description="Free mentoring for product marketers and technical writers.">
  <section class="mentor-page">
    <h1>I Mentor For Free!</h1>
    <h2>Empowering Product Marketers & Technical Writers to Grow, Lead, and Succeed</h2>
    <p>It can be hard to get meaningful support when you don't have the right title or network. This is my way of making that support a little easier to access. My mission is to help you elevate your skills.</p>

    <h3>Together, we can:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Clarify Complex Ideas</strong> – Simplify technical concepts for any audience.</li>
      <li><strong>Strengthen Strategy</strong> – Build smarter go-to-market and content strategies.</li>
      <li><strong>Refine Messaging</strong> – Craft clear, compelling narratives that resonate.</li>
      <li><strong>Master Project Management</strong> – Plan, prioritize, and execute with precision.</li>
      <li><strong>Choose the Right Tools, Workflows &amp; Processes</strong> – Select and implement to boost efficiency.</li>
      <li><strong>Advance Your Career</strong> – Navigate role transitions and career growth.</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>There is no time limit on quality mentoring. We start with one meeting, and take it from there.</strong></p>

    <p>I genuinely love mentoring. It's not a side interest or a leadership checkbox—it's core to how I operate, both as a person and a professional. Supporting people as they grow into PMM or technical writing roles, build confidence, or rethink their path is something I care about deeply.</p>

    <!-- Booking calendar embed goes here -->
    <a href="/contact">Book a Free Session</a>
  </section>
</Base>
